teaching/=0APosted     : March 28, 2026 at 12:23 pm=0AAuthor     : Blair Fi=
x=0ATags       : cueing, decline of reading ability, decoding, history of w=
riting, literacy, NAEP, phonemic awareness, phonics, reading score gap, str=
uctured literacy, whole language, why reading is hard to learn=0ACategories=
 : Uncategorized=0A=0AYour browser does not support the audio tag.=0A=0ADow=
nload: PDF ( https://economicsfromthetopdown.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03=
/fix_reading_20260328.pdf )  | EPUB ( https://sciencedesk.economicsfromthet=
