</blockquote>=0A=
<p style=3D"font-family: -apple-system,system-ui,blinkmacsystemfont,&quot;S=
egoe UI&quot;,Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot=
;,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; line-height: 1.=
7; padding: 0; color: #101517; margin-bottom: 24px;">Given the immense temp=
oral gap between simple picture drawing and formal writing, we can infer th=
at ancient humans struggled greatly with this problem. But they eventually =
discovered a good solution, which was to use pictures in a more abstract wa=
y. Instead of using pictures to represent real-world things, they used pict=
ures to represent <em>linguistic sounds</em>.</p>=0A=
<p style=3D"font-family: -apple-system,system-ui,blinkmacsystemfont,&quot;S=
egoe UI&quot;,Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot=
;,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; line-height: 1.=
7; padding: 0; color: #101517; margin-bottom: 24px;">This method is called =
the <a target=3D"_blank" href=3D"https://economicsfromthetopdown.com?action=
=3Duser_content_redirect&amp;uuid=3Dc903f748f441dde43ddc59d88c84a501f5b00ed=
f219232eb37b6d10c212d6299&amp;blog_id=3D160901125&amp;post_id=3D14975&amp;u=
ser_id=3D259268523&amp;subs_id=3D754610508&amp;signature=3D557daf36916302d2=
5a2a5f07c4026bca&amp;email_name=3Dnew-post&amp;user_email=3Dinfo@woodfine.c=
o&amp;encoded_url=3DaHR0cHM6Ly9lbi53aWtpcGVkaWEub3JnL3dpa2kvUmVidXMjUmVidXN=
fcHJpbmNpcGxl&amp;email_id=3D2ccc018290498254a8f7ab6d227747ea" style=3D"col=
or: #3858e9; text-decoration: underline;">=E2=80=98rebus principle=E2=80=99=
</a>, and it works as follows. To encode a message that has no simple assoc=
iated image, we first decompose the message into sounds. Then we map these =
sounds onto a set of simple images. For example, if we combine the image of=
 a bee and a leaf (as shown in Figure&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://economicsfrom=
thetopdown.com?action=3Duser_content_redirect&amp;uuid=3Ded954c07f034a12430=
dab5f7c4e8ec4d5ee90092409ab16234bcc65b516fc853&amp;blog_id=3D160901125&amp;=
