;,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; line-height: 1.=
7; padding: 0; color: #101517; margin-bottom: 24px;">The point here is that=
 well into adulthood, the main driver of functional illiteracy is the inabi=
lity to decode words =E2=80=94 an inability that whole-language teaching ac=
tively promotes.</p>=0A=
