7; padding: 0; color: #101517; margin-bottom: 24px;">The results of this te=
aching experiment were nothing short of dramatic. Mississippi=E2=80=99s fou=
rth-grade reading scores were vaulted from worst in class to among the top =
ten. But more interesting, in my view, is the structure of this <a target=
=3D"_blank" href=3D"https://economicsfromthetopdown.com?action=3Duser_conte=
nt_redirect&amp;uuid=3D14fbee8ee7723e92b77c881ae2c2e748c032784bdf6363d92ab1=
6e69b36236ab&amp;blog_id=3D160901125&amp;post_id=3D14975&amp;user_id=3D2592=
